name: U.F.O (Dackss)
description:
Play as an alien in their U.F.O (Unreal Fishing Object) as they try to catch as many types of fish as possible. Simply click when a fish is on the line and catch it! Use money you earn to buy upgrades to get even rarer fish! This is a short, simple and chill fishing  game made in 72 hours for MiniJam#91. 

--Credits--

Code and Art done by me (Dackss)

Music by morocolombres from Pixabay
